WEBVTT

00:00:18.509 --> 00:00:23.005
The ceiling isn't real. It's bewitched
to look like the night sky.

00:00:23.347 --> 00:00:26.217
<i>I read about it
in Hogwarts, A History.</i>

00:00:39.488 --> 00:00:42.323
Will you wait along here, please?

00:00:43.742 --> 00:00:46.529
Now, before we begin...

00:00:46.745 --> 00:00:49.994
...Professor Dumbledore would like
to say a few words.

